az m'hot undz aroysgeshikt,

00:22:36.961 --> 00:22:39.759
nu, zenen mir geven azoy NESCHASTNe.

00:22:40.137 --> 00:22:42.763
az mir zenen gekumen tsu forn,

00:22:43.090 --> 00:22:46.391
