00:23:02.074 --> 00:23:03.063
yo.

00:23:03.441 --> 00:23:06.052
az ikh bin geven tsu zey farkoyft,

00:23:06.141 --> 00:23:10.877
zenen mir, fleg er mikh opfirn un fleg mikh brengen.

00:23:10.877 --> 00:23:12.845
ikh hob gelozt di kinder.

00:23:12.845 --> 00:23:16.947
mayn shviger iz gezesn funem nayntsetn yor

00:23:16.947 --> 00:23:24.017
bizkele GITLER iz arayn. ven GITLER ⟨z-,⟩ kumt nit, efsher volt zi nokh geven gelebt. a gezunte yidene a sheyne,

00:23:24.017 --> 00:23:26.722
nor zi iz gezesn; zi hot zikh nit gekent rirn.

00:23:27.184 --> 00:23:31.413
fleg ikh, ⟨iz zi, mir,⟩ zenen mir geven,

00:23:31.673 --> 00:23:33.489
ikh un, ⟨un,⟩

00:23:33.580 --> 00:23:40.307
 di shtume. ⟨zi iz shoyn⟩ geven lebn undz, derfar vos di shviger hobn mir gelozt az m'hot undz aroysgeshikt,

00:23:40.431 --> 00:23:43.564
mit ⟨kirkes⟩ un mit, mi- mit alemen.

00:23:43.755 --> 00:23:46.871
 fleg er mikh f- firn ahin.

00:23:47.164 --> 00:23:50.212
fleg ikh im zogn, "PAN VRONSKe,

00:23:50.303 --> 00:23:52.322
UNK ⟨mikh⟩ do lozn."

00:23:54.792 --> 00:23:57.047
fleg er zogn, er hot keyn deye nit.

00:23:57.981 --> 00:23:59.914
nor ile oyfdernakht

00:23:59.914 --> 00:24:03.476
flegn zikh tsunoyfnemen Rumener un daytshn,

00:24:04.562 --> 00:24:07.222
me fleg praven vetsherinkes,

00:24:07.718 --> 00:24:10.982
un mikh hot men gebrakht, ikh zol helfn in kikh,

00:24:10.982 --> 00:24:13.666
nor m'hot nit gezogt az ikh bin a yidishke.

00:24:13.666 --> 00:24:18.824
nor m'hot, ⟨⟩, derkent: me fleg onton hintn a znak un fornt a znak, ⟨az mir⟩,

00:24:17.370 --> 00:24:18.933
vos, a gele late?

00:24:18.824 --> 00:24:20.300
az mir zenen yidn.

00:24:22.095 --> 00:24:25.632
flegn mir zitsn un, bin ikh geven dort.

00:24:25.639 --> 00:24:27.421
fleg ⟨er⟩ zogn,

00:24:27.445 --> 00:24:37.479
hot men gemakht di vetsherinke. m'hot gebrokhn teler, az di royte veln arayn demlt ven di, s'vet vaksn UNK.

00:24:36.017 --> 00:24:37.787
hor oyf der hant.

00:24:38.228 --> 00:24:41.259
nu, az di royte zenen ober arayn,

00:24:41.518 --> 00:24:47.083
iz, hot men zey bald... s'iz geven go- katsapes:

00:24:47.083 --> 00:24:50.628
eyne iz geven a UCHITEL'NITSe, eyne iz geven a VRACH,

00:24:50.628 --> 00:24:54.614
hobn zey gearbet in shkole bay zey.

00:24:54.900 --> 00:24:59.349
un er fleg geyn in shkole arayn a P- PRAVITEL'.

00:24:59.642 --> 00:25:02.116
fleg er zogn,

00:25:02.207 --> 00:25:10.526
s'vet dem⟨lt⟩ arayn di day- di royte ven s'vet kumen di, ven s'vet ⟨bakn oyf der hant pirozhkes⟩.

00:25:10.577 --> 00:25:13.878
iz er gekumen tsu gey- az zey zenen gekumen,

00:25:14.070 --> 00:25:17.827
hot men bald fir ire arestirt:

00:25:17.935 --> 00:25:23.787
s'iz geven der VRONSKe un nokh dray. m'hot zey bald arestirt.

00:25:24.516 --> 00:25:29.910
UNK azoy o a tog. k- esn iz nito vos tsu gibn di kinder.

00:25:30.118 --> 00:25:33.183
shtub iz kalt; fun di vent rint.

00:25:34.692 --> 00:25:37.757
 vos zol men, ton?

00:25:37.982 --> 00:25:42.144
kumt tsu geyn di VRONSKikhe un nokh eyne.

00:25:43.365 --> 00:25:47.617
"GENECHKA, ⟨SHCHO VY DAETE DITYAM KUSHAT'⟩?"

00:25:47.617 --> 00:25:50.045
UNK vos zol ikh zey gibn?

00:25:50.045 --> 00:25:51.611
"⟨IDI ZA MNOY⟩."

00:25:52.410 --> 00:25:55.255
