00:25:55.255 --> 00:25:57.042
"⟨IDI ZA MNOY⟩."

00:25:57.042 --> 00:25:59.390
hot men genemen un m'hot ongeshikt

00:25:59.818 --> 00:26:05.094
mir m- m- kukuruzene mel un broyt un mir zenen gekumen aheym.

00:26:05.978 --> 00:26:12.917
hot men mikh aroysgerufn un m'hot zey bald arestirt. s'hot men undz aroysge- mikh aroysgerufn in N.K.V.D. arayn.

00:26:12.917 --> 00:26:15.619
m'hot undz aroysgerufn, hob ikh ongehoybn tsu dertseyln.

00:26:15.619 --> 00:26:18.982
"ober ⟨az ir't⟩ geyn mit zey oyf ⟨OCHNAYA STAVKA⟩..."

00:26:19.107 --> 00:26:25.125
zog ikh, "nu, vos zhe hot ir moyre, az ikh'l nit dertseyln? nor ir zolt, hitn mikh az zey zoln mikh nit hargenen."

00:26:27.561 --> 00:26:30.204
kumen tsu geyn, zitst un UNK...

00:26:30.328 --> 00:26:33.882
iz er arayngegan, der, VRONSKe.

00:26:34.024 --> 00:26:38.505
⟨zog ikh im,⟩ "ZDRAVSTVUYTE, PAN VRONSKe. ZDRAVSTVUYTE, PAN VRONSKe."

00:26:38.935 --> 00:26:42.742
"YA ZHE NE PAN. YA ZHE TOVARISHCH VRONSKe."

00:26:43.390 --> 00:26:47.403
nu, m'hot zey azoy lang gehaltn un m'hot zey oykh aroysgeshikt.

00:26:47.403 --> 00:26:49.938
vuhin m'hot zey aroysgeshikt, veys ikh nit,

00:26:49.938 --> 00:26:53.226
un mit dem iz dos UNK gevorn.

00:26:53.226 --> 00:26:58.659
un azoy hobn mir zikh ustroyet dos lebn, un mir hobn gelebt, un s'iz geven UNK.

00:26:57.902 --> 00:27:00.579
